Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:05.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}This is a fate that brought us here watch my long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:15.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Feel like I am falling into the flame of lies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Tell me what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:22.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Trying not to step back to where I used to belong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Looking for the escape from pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:29.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}I will cross my fingers hoping not to be sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}約束したんだ君とその希望に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:36.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Get in the raid Get ready for the time to come
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}浮かび上がるシルエット追いかけ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Drop down the reason why I'm standing here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}May be it's already too late to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:52.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}運命としてかかげた灯を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:57.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}What if I could right my wrongs and save you from the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:07.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0\fs82.5}It's not enough It's not enough for me to break the rule upon this world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:12.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}I will never gonna leave you never wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}we'll make it in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:20.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}Not backing down for real I won't trace someone else's life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fsp0}I know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:05.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}命運帶我們走到了這裡 見識我的豪賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:15.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}仿佛落入了謊言的烈火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.44,0:03:18.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}請告訴我 你想讓我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:22.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}為了保護我所在的家園
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我尋找著逃脫苦難的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:29.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我握拳祈禱不會有人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我保證過不會放棄你和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:36.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}做好準備 直面必將到來的侵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}追趕著腦海裡浮現的倩影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}捨棄掉孤獨戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}想奪回一切也許為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:52.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}但也不要丟失命運給你的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:57.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}如果我能改掉錯誤 救你於水火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:07.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}那也不夠我去打破這個世界的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:12.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我不會再丟下你 不會再失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我們一定能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:20.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我決不後退 決不成為別人理想的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我知道我該過怎樣的人生
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.25,0:27:21.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}壊れないように優しく抱いて　溶けて涙流す
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.55,0:27:27.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}そんな氷の人形みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.49,0:27:32.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}なれないから
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.54,0:27:44.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}もう逃げない　知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.33,0:27:48.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}強く　I believe…believe in you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.09,0:27:52.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}きっと一番の約束の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:56.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}痛いくらい握って離さない
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.86,0:28:02.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}わがままな今連れて　誰のものでもない未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.62,0:28:05.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}そこから始めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.33,0:28:15.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}空を掴む(夢の欠片)　祈りの手を(指先まで)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.79,0:28:20.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}伸ばすかぎり(生けるかぎり)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.85,0:28:28.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}そこに本当はあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.25,0:27:21.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}我當不了一隻冰做的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.55,0:27:27.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}將你小心翼翼地抱在懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.49,0:27:32.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}眼眶裡融化出晶瑩的淚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.54,0:27:44.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}所以我不會再逃避  我想去了解
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.33,0:27:48.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}我會堅定地…堅定地相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.09,0:27:52.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}當初最放在心底裡的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:56.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}我會緊緊把握  絕不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.86,0:28:02.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}帶著任性的現在  從此邁步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.62,0:28:05.33,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}向著沒有人能把控的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.33,0:28:15.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}抓住空中(夢的碎片)  握掌祈求(併攏指尖)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.79,0:28:20.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}用力伸出手臂(直到生命的盡頭)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.85,0:28:28.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be8}我終將發現真相
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
